verbose_text: To determine if CK666 inhibits Dictyostelium Arp2/3 complex activity and the time span of efficacy, Dictyostelium cells constitutively expressing GFP-Arp3 were incubated with 100 muM CK666, with 0.2% DMSO / media as the solvent control, or media only, for different lengths of time, followed by fixation and staining with TRITC labeled phalloidin to localize F-actin.
